OL,3,CAurigny CEO defends Guernsey's airline
OL,4,Csaying it's faring better than others
OL,6,FThis message was not welcomed by some
OL,7,Faudience members, including Barry Cash
OL,8,Ffrom Guernsey Aviation Action Group,
OL,9,Fwho said: "There were no questions
OL,10,Fbeing asked about why are we just
OL,11,Frelying on listening to the present
OL,12,Fincumbents when we should be standing
OL,13,Fback and looking objectively on what
OL,14,Fwe really need."
